schedule a tour please contact us today contact us did you know for every person diagnosed with alzheimer’s disease there are  to  others – family coworkers and neighbors – who are directly impacted learn more evidencebased low residenttocaregiver partner ratio with innovative evidencebased continual quality improvement staff training programming and staffing models i see abes garden becoming the leading american center in alzheimers care and contributing to research into the causes of alzheimers and other dementias  it will be a leader in what is becoming a major medical problem and im just glad we can help in some way – jim daniell sign up for our newsletter stay uptodate on the progress of abes garden email  leave this field blank abes garden is now open be among the first to access the care the science and the lifestyle offered by abes garden for more information about abes garden or to schedule a tour please contact us today contact us michael d shmerling cpa executive profile  biography  bloomberg july    am et capital markets company overview of xmi high growth development fund llc snapshotpeople  overviewboard memberscommittees executive profile michael d shmerling cpamanaging partner xmi high growth development fund llcagetotal calculated compensationthis person is connected to  board members in  different organizations across  different industriessee board relationships background mr michael d shmerling also known as mike cpa has been an executive vice president of kroll inc since september   mr shmerling serves as a managing partner of xmi high growth development fund llc he served as the chief executive officer at xmi holdings inc he began his career in  at ernst  ernst he founded companies include transcor america inc corrections partners inc amicus legal staffing and background america inc he served as the  chief operating officer of kroll risk consulting services inc since august  he serves as the chairman of the board at xmi holdings inc localshares 