al holdings within the church streetmidtown corridor he owns more than  square feet of multitenant office properties plus several acres of land and standalone properties available for redevelopmentreach getahn ward at  and on twitter getahn  connecttweetlinkedin  commentemailmoreread or share this story httptnnewskrkab